{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 ============================================================\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 5.\tx360\tab Operating Modes\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Automatic Mode: - Control loop active - Feed runs when WIRE_FEED is TRUE and no fault exists - Recovery controlled by PID (optional feedforward compensation)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Manual Mode: - PID disabled - Motors controlled only by local buttons\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 ============================================================\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 6.\tx360\tab Control System\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Feed frequency:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 f_feed_steps_per_sec = (WIRE_FEED_RATE \u215? STEPS_PER_SPOOL_REV) / 60\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Dancer measurement: x_cm = a \u215? ADC + b x_f = (1 \u8722? \u945?)x_f + \u945?x\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 PID: e = DANCER_SETPOINT \u8722? x_f I = clamp(I + KI \u215? e \u215? dt, \u8722?Imax, +Imax) D = KD \u215? (e \u8722? e_prev)/dt u = KP \u215? e + I + D\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Recovery command: f_takeup = f_feed + u (or feedforward variant if enabled)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 ============================================================\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 7.\tx360\tab Fault Handling\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 WIRE_FAULT asserted if: - x_f < MINIMUM_DANCER_POSITION - OR x_f > MAXIMUM_DANCER_POSITION - OR ADC invalid\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 On fault: - Motors disabled within MISSING INFO ms - Fault latched until cleared\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 ============================================================\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 8.\tx360\tab MODBUS Register Map\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Holding Registers:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 40001 WIRE_FEED_RATE (rev/min) 40002 DANCER_SETPOINT (cm \u215?1000) 40003 MIN_DANCER_POS (cm \u215?1000) 40004 MAX_DANCER_POS (cm \u215?1000) 40005 PID_KP 40006 PID_KI 40007 PID_KD 40008 FAULT_CLEAR 40009 SPOOL_RESET (optional)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Coils:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 00001 WIRE_FEED\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Input Registers:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 30001 DANCER_POSITION (cm \u215?1000) 30002 WATER_RESISTIVITY (raw ADC) 30003 FAULT_CODE\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Discrete Inputs:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 10001 WIRE_FAULT 10002 AUTO_MODE\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 ============================================================\par}
